Package: openneuro
Title: Programmatic Access to OpenNeuro Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
  )
Description: Search, explore, and download datasets from 'OpenNeuro'
    <https://openneuro.org>, the largest open neuroimaging data repository.
    Queries the 'OpenNeuro' GraphQL API to discover datasets by modality,
    diagnosis, or keyword; inspect snapshots, files, and subject lists;
    and download full datasets or selected subsets via HTTPS, Amazon S3,
    or 'DataLad'. Downloaded data are cached locally so subsequent
    requests skip already-fetched files.
